{"tid":1107360,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個對付Freeride.嘅方法","createTime":"2019-04-15T07:54:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T02:27:47.000Z","uid":241751,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"7b08acc455ac4268699ba094bae87c62c012df61","tid":1107360,"uid":241751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:54:34.000Z","msg":"如題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚嬲 得返3日時間中有成2/3 part未搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負責個條友由第一日叫佢做野就話病 病到今日乜春都冇做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講好話今朝會搞掂自己個part又係9 up嘅<br />\n點算 又冇得分開交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但咁大份野又冇理由亦冇時間得2-3條友做曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇咩方法可以迫條友做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e633032b17866bcf8126aead792c3614e694083","tid":1107360,"uid":225443,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"攬抄"},{"pid":"dafc6bc6494821e97e786864340edfd61e39b81a","tid":1107360,"uid":242226,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:12:02.000Z","msg":"攞曬證據同lecturer或者tutor講<br />\n同其他組員分咗佢個part做，做完唔落佢名"},{"pid":"08723db411130b57ca78ebdd6d9214ac66d6f518","tid":1107360,"uid":1482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"直接比1%佢未算囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16761213307c4bd8c4e91f7b566d6cd1dea442d7","tid":1107360,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"依家熄連登自己做埋 cap圖email prof踢佢出組"},{"pid":"9814c4008b97341bc3c23eecb783eba83b83d50e","tid":1107360,"uid":243393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:20:16.000Z","msg":"開一頁分工表，每頁打翻做個條友個名，<br />\n再email教授問有冇得踢佢出組。<br />\n或者直接份野唔好落佢名，<br />\n到時問咩事直接話條友冇做過野。"},{"pid":"55cb41c35da7dcdb0b4e1a0fce8e4e8123f17e54","tid":1107360,"uid":247934,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"Present改過份佢未睇過既PPT"},{"pid":"cf50d868f9b01a660cd2df3195102ae6c0302969","tid":1107360,"uid":239565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"同教授報寸"},{"pid":"5c683aba3b6930dae759b54402a707b0264d5a1b","tid":1107360,"uid":247694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T10:42:32.000Z","msg":"留名樓主死死地氣做埋 繼續俾人freeride<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a5a8abf52c38da4605682b56d711434534e06a","tid":1107360,"uid":93890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"其實仲有3日 <br />\n如果佢駁話唸住聽日做咁點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c657eec574fffc0d3f64a13f896404541f2f3c3","tid":1107360,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T14:05:37.000Z","msg":"cap低通訊記錄，send比prof, 等佢處理"},{"pid":"34bca5bdda12a79ab9f02654de4a4c15a8638b83","tid":1107360,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e401d45fb20715b04fae95a06c3e716b4a681f","tid":1107360,"uid":119145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T14:18:40.000Z","msg":"屌你 仲有3日時間 就咪撚煩我啦"},{"pid":"06b5f